<div class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family:'Verdana', 'sans-serif';font-size:9pt;">Posted by <a title="author profile" href="http://www.blogger.com/profile/10166141371599425570">NVP </a>at <a title="permanent link" href="http://nguyenvanphu.blogspot.com/2013/12/bitcoin-1.html">5:53 PM</a> </span></div>
